5220 PRINT (7)@(H0+5),FNB$(A0$(21,3)),"  ",A0$(11,10),@(H0+31),A[0]:M1$,@(H0+49),A[1]:M1$,@(H0+67),A[0]-A[2]-A[1]:M1$
